Fan Yue.

21:40.010 --> 21:41.400
Saya bawa awak balik ke rumah.

21:42.870 --> 21:44.210
Baik.

21:48.120 --> 21:48.950
Shuo.

22:02.660 --> 22:03.510
Shuo.

22:50.070 --> 22:51.240
Cantiknya.

22:51.480 --> 22:52.530
Cepat tengok.

